{"type": "article", "id": 24931, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-05T07:03:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 25795, "name": "Apparatu"}, {"id": 25156, "name": "CKIE"}, {"id": 25796, "name": "FEW"}, {"id": 3812, "name": "丰田"}, {"id": 25797, "name": "Lorenzo Lee"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120312ptZTfeVGEJ2oIxqU.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>student projects  by VIA Design School</h2>\n<p>这组家具来自丹麦 VIA 大学的学生，一共 12 种，在今年的斯德哥尔摩家具展上展出。他们都运用木头等材料打造生活中常见的家具，有自己个性和特征。比如挂在墙上的半圆形置物盒，可以像抽屉一样拉开，造型简洁而带着自然的特征。一款沙发有两个像花瓣一样的环绕式靠背，一大一小相互交错，赋予了沙发柔和自然的色彩。<a href=\"http://en.via.dk/programmes/design/gallery/stockholm-furniture-fair-2016\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182049UObBJhyqrTDWRzdM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182050q0g13tINPVnYQJuO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182050JPz6yfB5gcAsT7hE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182051TM3XBHFCZe2KcV9J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182051FDZuCbq8hTt5AKJY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>circuit &amp; tassle by Apparatu</h2>\n<p>这是纽约的设计工作室 Apparatu 展出的两款灯具，都采用了黄铜灯罩来体现古典。其中一款灯是椭圆形的，两两垂直错位形成一个较大的灯，有音阶的韵律。另一款灯是在黄铜灯罩下装上圆筒形的玻璃瓶，可以是单独的灯罩和玻璃瓶或者一个大灯罩下很多玻璃瓶，都像是垂下来的光束，拥有明暗变化和质感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182052OQ2eSNGIA4fBxrhM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70415648\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182052rpSF6KbR8XxkQ4HI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70537897\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060718205301jdPuLwINxaytXE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63447433\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071820536izvKSCl8nTNIHVh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70415648\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182053oDESP2eW1A5gxp9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70415648\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Garland Rubber Band by Lorenzo Lee</h2>\n<p>这是一个用来捆扎的橡胶环，按照刻好的纹路向两边拉伸就形成菱形的网格，刚好捆扎一张圆筒状的纸。它也可以套在吃了一半的薯片上，成为密封的办法。如果更用力拉伸就形成三个连起来的圆环，可以用来分类。这个简单巧妙的小工具也很实用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182054VQe60GTnxD5uhZwk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182054rNsCfxTKla60DuVA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182055Y1vxKHW9mC4RUdQD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071820562ECuPxqbsOmIHaDB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182056nKt0JO3FMbTjCzYo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Nixie Clock by CKIE</h2>\n<p>这是一盏非常酷炫的数字钟，它是用亮灯的形式来指示时间。4 个椭圆形的玻璃罩里用灯丝拼出了从 0 到 9 的数字形状，每到相应的时间就会点亮相应的灯，隐隐像一团燃烧的火焰，适合放在酒吧等环境中。它也可以作为夜灯使用。有枫木和花梨木两种外壳，分别售价 235 美元、285 美元，<a href=\"http://www.ckie.com/products/nixie-clocks#.VwJ00sdhyS8\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182056Tgjc9HLZE27R5FWK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182057xnt5kRZGhKTzQpDu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182057nGuXKJRbgPhNetOi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182058Zy4GpJUWjOA6tKBh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182058P3mUytR0wFe27Lns.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Setsuna by 丰田</h2>\n<p>这是丰田在米兰家具展上展出的木质电动概念车，是用 86 块雪松木板材拼接成的。从正面看它的外壳在车盖和车身上分别是竖条和横条的纹路，颜色有深浅的不规则变化，没有喷漆，很柔和。木块的拼接方式类似于榫卯，不需要使用钉子，设计师希望它能够根据时代变化，当有技术和外形的改变时也能实现替换。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182059JUhPjuKglA2tzT3i.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182059ew1AITipgP7FhmCM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182100k3E5VDBYgu4W6SlQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182100waz0o9Wg1CAYbV6v.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182101WgtdNiFcOo1j4LfE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182101pftGeMRz4gjvElJu.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>SIBBARPS HUSBRYGGERI by FEW</h2>\n<p>这个来自瑞典的啤酒包装上有着一只令人印象深刻的鸟，瓶盖上是鸟头的图案，瓶身的贴纸和装啤酒的纸箱上是张开翅膀的鸟的剪影，使得整体包装完整且有强烈的辨识度。鸟的图案指的是酿造的地方 Sibbarp，除此之外也没有其他的图案，给人带来一种传统手工的感受。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182102yzRTPWqFtgwhai90.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182103ETdcurpaRPGzSVwf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75049702\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182103eOoVtAbkUTmRgPr5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65308151\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182104Asliq8JCryHfx3bc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182104pNXGWIQet51jwaKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}